      <hedline>
        <hl1>A Clean Sweep</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Denise Giardina letter disputes article disparaging Harry Potter books (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>Thanks for clearing all those awful Harry Potter books out of the way. Now we can concentrate on Danielle Steel, E. Lynn Harris, Catherine Coulter, Tim LaHaye, Julie Garwood and Jackie Collins. It's good to know someone is looking out for the arts.</p>
        <p>Denise Giardina  Charleston, W.Va.</p>
      </block>
